- **Debounce**: Uses `useEffect` + `setTimeout` (300ms). The effect cleanup (`return () => clearTimeout(timer)`) automatically clears any pending timer both on unmount and before scheduling a new one on the next keystroke.
- **Searching indicator**: Set immediately when a non-empty trimmed value is detected; cleared only inside the timeout callback.
